msgid "Rugged Villager"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132_Rugged Villager"
msgid "They say the road into town is finally clear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144_Rugged Villager"
msgid "There's no reason for you to stay here now. You should get out of here as soon as you can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168_Rugged Villager"
msgid "You're the one Okudera-san brought back, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180_Rugged Villager"
msgid "Normally I'd tell you to move on as soon as you can, but the road into town is closed because of the snow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192_Rugged Villager"
msgid "You just stay out of trouble until the road is clear, now. No idea how long that'll take, though."
msgstr ""

